data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Attention all buyers! MOTIVATED SELLER, this Longleaf gem welcomes all offers from motivated buyers. Picture yourself in this pristine two-story home in a charming community with picket fences and inviting front porches. This impeccably maintained 3BD/2BA home with a loft and two-car garage boasts style and comfort. Features include wood-look ceramic tile, a gourmet kitchen with stainless steel appliances and granite countertops, and a spa-like master bath. Longleaf offers walkable living, parks, trails, and sports facilities, plus top-rated schools within the community. Don't miss out—schedule your tour today!
